==English==
===Etymology===
From Japanese [[山葵]] ([[わさび]], wasabi).

===Pronunciation===
*[[IPA]]: /wə'sɑ:bi/
*[[w:AHD|AHD]]: wä'sə-bē, wə-sä'-bē

===Noun===
'''wasabi''' ([[uncountable]])

#green Japanese [[condiment]] made from the plant ''Wasabia japonica''.
#imitation of the condiment made from [[horseradish]] with green dye.

